						<h1>感冒糖漿「卡」尿？膀胱無力男子　喝到得揹尿袋一周</h1>

						
						<div id="reporter_info">
														
						<a href="/home/coraline/Documents/Corpus/readability/corpus/zh/html/20120112_www.nownews.com_bc1bd14d807d8cd9400833fab9f4353de5affae799096d1764c77f47" target="_blank">
							<img class="reporter-thumb" src="http://static.nownews.com/newspic/1814/s1814520.jpg"/>
						</a>
						<h2>陳鈞凱</h2>
						<p>2012年1月12日 11:06</p>
						</div>
						
						
						
						<div class="box_1">
							
							
							
							
							<div class="story_photo">
